Yep. So let's say you have `_OldSlice` and `_NewSlice`. Going in, you'll have a version of ONNX with `Slice` mapped to `_OldSlice`. Then, to move to NewSlice, you write this changelog entry:

```
ChangelogEntry {
  removed = "Slice"
  added = OperatorBinding {
    op_type = "Slice",
    op_def = "_NewSlice",
  }
}
```

